Neo Retros

Written by : Gareth Saunders

He Friday feeling being wasted losing everything you lacked
You're looking leaner meaner tougher looking like a real cool cat
Taking bets on silent killers perking up your empty heart
The second hand is motionless I like to watch you fall apart

You see a parody and parallel[ˈpærəˌlel] to everything you felt
Where all the spiritual[ˈspɪrɪtʃʊəl] and dutiful will offer up their help
They're waving crosses beads and bibles saying how your life could be
Disbelief in your reasons disbelief in what you see

Cut but you don't bleed


Now there's a rocket in your pocket seen an effect but no cause
And all the energy in vengeance[ˈvendʒəns] sees you opening old sores
The world of jokers brokers mockers say you're rotten to the skin
And all those bones that creak below it sign confessions of their sins

Now there's a legend of a legend and a classic being made
But all the legend's are just legends and the classics seem to fade
You see the second hand rotating[rəʊˈteɪtɪŋ] like a turbine[ˈtɜːbaɪn] in a gale[ɡeɪl]
Say goodbye to yester morrow where the challengers all failled 

A legend of a legend never

————————————————————————————————————————————————————————————————————————————————————————————————————————————————————————————————————
leaner meaner tougher:又瘦又吝啬又强硬
Taking bets on silent killers perking up your empty heart
在沉默的杀手身上下注，让你空虚的心振作起来

second hand 第二只手
motionless  不动的；静止的
fall apart  崩溃

parody    滑稽（或夸张）地模仿
parallel  与…同时发生；与…相关联；与…相当；与…平行


spiritual 高尚的
dutiful   有责任感的

crosses beads and bibles  十字架珠子和圣经

seen an effect but no cause 看到了效果，但没有原因

vengeance   复仇
sore        伤痛处

jokers brokers mockers  小丑、破坏者、嘲笑者
rotten to the skin  腐烂到皮肤上

And all those bones that creak below it sign confessions of their sins
所有在它下面吱吱作响的骨头都标志着他们的罪过的忏悔
Now there's a legend of a legend and a classic being made
现在有一个传奇、经典的传说正在被创造

rotate  旋转
turbine 涡轮机
gale  大风

yester  昨日的
morrow  早上；清晨

————————————————————————————————————————————————————————————————————————————————————————————————————————————————————————————————————


